title: Big Debate In Amy's House Over Her Daughter Cooking While Home Alone + Lunchbox Goes Christmas Caroling In Late January + New Evidence In Eddie Seeing Taylor Swift Driving
itunes:title: Big Debate In Amy's House Over Her Daughter Cooking While Home Alone + Lunchbox Goes Christmas Caroling In Late January + New Evidence In Eddie Seeing Taylor Swift Driving
description:
Amy's 12-year-old daughter Stachira really loves having responsibility at the house. She also gets really invested at cooking times. So Amy decided to teach her daughter how to cook on their gas stove, but her husband isn’t having it. Lunchbox went Christmas caroling at almost the end of January. He went singing to people’s houses that still have Christmas lights on. New evidence has emerged about Eddie and if he really did see Taylor Swift driving her own car in town.
